build.description: Deep Sea Visitor is the recommended engine. This build focuses on boosting Ellen's Basic Attack damage, after triggering Shatter on enemies, and leverages Woodpecker Electro's CRIT Rate buff typical for DPS play.

Maximizes Billy's damage by using his Ultimate after a Chain Attack for a heavy burst, then maintains consistent damage with Basic Attacks. Prioritizes ATK main stat, Physical DMG secondary, and CRIT on the 4-piece. Puffer Electro is a situational support pick to boost ATK after his Ultimate.

This build leverage Alice's frequent Assault triggers to boost her damage and provide extra buffs. Focus on maximizing ATK, Anomaly Proficiency, and Anomaly Mastery to get the most out of her Additional Ability. Aim for at least 140 Anomaly Mastery as a minimum â€” each point above this threshold increases Alice's Anomaly Proficiency while her Additional Ability is active.
mainStats: 5 - Physical Damage Bonus OR Drilling Rate

build.description: Stun / Daze-focused build. Maximizes Anby's ability to Daze while still providing damage from Basic Attacks and EX. Primary W-Engine is The Restrained ; uses Shockstar Disco 4-piece + Swing Jazz 2-piece disc set.

Maximizes Anton's damage during Burst Mode and his Shock-triggered damage. Uses Dawn's Bloom (4-piece) for the large ATK buff and Swing Jazz (2-piece) for additional DPS synergy. Prioritize CRIT Rate so Burst hits reliably crit.
mainStats: 5 - Electric Damage Bonus OR Drilling Rate

build.description: Focuses on ATK and Energy Regen to maximize her support buffs. Best W-Engine: Elegant Vanity. Alternative W-Engines: Kaboom the Cannon, Bashful Demon, The Vault. Use Astral Voice (4-piece) + Swing Jazz (2-piece). 6-piece main stat should be different from the W-Engine.

Defense-oriented Ben build. Maximizes the shield HP Ben provides and raises his ATK via DEF scaling. Prioritizes Energy Regen so Ben can use EX Special Attacks more often to maintain shield uptime. Swing Jazz (4pc) provides Energy Regen and Chain Attack DMG while Soul Rock (2pc) increases DEF.
